---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DarkHeader from '../../components/DarkHeader.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Sewing &amp; Making — Cooper Minehart"
  description="Sewing, serging, and hands-on making as a counterweight to research work."
>
  <DarkHeader>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-10">
      <a href="/hobbies" class="text-sm text-forest-400 hover:text-forest-300 mb-6 inline-block">← Hobbies</a>
      <p class="section-label-light mb-3">Hobbies</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-white">Sewing &amp; Making</h1>
    </div>
  </DarkHeader>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10 pb-24">
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg mb-10 aspect-[16/9] bg-stone-100">
      <img
        src="/photos/wallet.jpeg"
        alt="Handmade wallet"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-[#333] leading-relaxed">

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Bike Bags from Reclaimed Material</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Pittsburgh has a materials reuse warehouse called PGH Reuse where people drop off
          fabric, hardware, foam, and whatever else they're not using. I've picked up zippers,
          an old punching bag that turned into cordura-weight material, and various straps and
          buckles. Found the leather for the wallet above too.
        </p>
        <video
          src="/photos/bike-bag.mov"
          autoplay
          muted
          loop
          playsinline
          class="w-full rounded-lg bg-stone-100"
        ></video>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Laser-Cut Patterns</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          CMU's Tech Spark has a laser engraver I've been using to cut fabric directly. It's
          faster and more repeatable than tracing and cutting by hand, and you can iterate on
          a fit adjustment without redrawing the whole thing.
        </p>
        <video
          src="/photos/cutting-patterns.mov"
          autoplay
          muted
          loop
          playsinline
          class="w-full rounded-lg bg-stone-100"
        ></video>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
